<BaseLayout title="About the Cake Maker" description="Discover the style and made-to-order approach behind GyulRose Cakes in Haywards Heath, West Sussex.">
  <section class="section"><div class="container about-grid"><div><p class="eyebrow">Independent cake maker</p><h1>Personal cakes, shaped around real celebrations.</h1><p class="lead">GyulRose Cakes creates made-to-order cakes in Haywards Heath, blending European-inspired flavours with personalised decoration for birthdays and meaningful occasions.</p><p>The current portfolio shows delicate floral piping, themed children's cakes, milestone designs, traditional layered cakes and detailed celebration pieces. Customers can bring a theme or use an existing cake as a starting point.</p><p>This local prototype deliberately avoids inventing the baker's personal history, qualifications or awards. A stronger final About page should be completed with her own story, portrait, experience and approved trust proof.</p><a class="button" href="/order/">Start a cake enquiry</a></div><img src="/images/cakes/9f3a8b4f-0855-49b4-ab7b-2211dcb04f32.jpeg" alt="Detailed portrait celebration cake by GyulRose Cakes" width="800" height="900" /></div></section>
</BaseLayout>
